---
title: Parmesan-Crumbed Chicken with Fries & Garlic Aioli
description: How can you improve on a classic chicken schnitzel? Add cheesy flavour right into the golden crumb coating! With colourful sides of fries and sautéed greens, this dish ended up even better than we imagined!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5fbc51f95349b913e85db5df-42235a1a.jpg
